cigaretteLicenseConfirmation.needHelpInfo: Contact DORES by [submitting a General Inquiry Form](https://www.nj.gov/treasury/revenue/revgencode.shtml).
cigaretteLicenseConfirmation.paymentSuccessfulInfo: Your application has been submitted to the NJ Division of Revenue and Enterprise Services (DORES) for review.
cigaretteLicenseConfirmation.whatHappensNextInfo: DORES will review your application and send a decision letter to the mailing address you provided.
cigaretteLicenseConfirmation.whatHappensNextBullet1: If approved, your license will be included with the letter
cigaretteLicenseConfirmation.whatHappensNextBullet2: If denied, the letter will explain the reason(s) for denial and how to reapply
cigaretteLicenseConfirmation.issuingAgency: **Issuing Agency:** NJ Division of Revenue and Enterprise Services
cigaretteLicenseConfirmation.cantCompleteFilingAlert: We received your payment, but we couldn’t complete your filing.
cigaretteLicenseConfirmation.cantCompleteFilingMessage1: Select “Try Again” and we’ll resend your filing details. **Do not** submit payment again.
cigaretteLicenseConfirmation.cantCompleteFilingMessage2: If you are still having trouble after trying again, select “Start a Live Chat” to get help.
